Hello, we appreciate you in advance for considering us on your next vehicle booking. To give you a bit of my background, I'm currently an high school teacher, who loves teaching. My number one teaching goal, is to make sure that my students have the information they need to be successful on their journey of life. 

I'm married to the love of my life. We have five children and two of them are still home in the nest, lol. We have truly been blessed to raise such wonderful children. Our youngest two are in middle/ high, currently enrolled in private school, due to these times of uncertainty. Which can sometimes be a bit challenging, but we will get them through high school and eventually college. 

This is why we started car 🚗 sharing, our goal is to pay for their current school tuition, and possible save money for college. One of them loves robotics 🤖 and the other basketball 🏀, you can understand our schedule as parents, here there and everywhere, lol.

Searching for me time, lol. I enjoy reading, walking, date night, family time and fun  adventures. We love people, so we also like to meet new people, lol. This adventure with car sharing has giving us an opportunity to meet some amazing people.
My name Slava. Here on Turo, I have 3 stunning cars, two are 2023 Corvette 3LT, and third is 2023 Cadillac Escalade Premium Luxury.

Crew Rentals is an expanding car rental company in the Metro Detroit Area. Increasing our fleet to Full size sedans, SUVs, Minivans & trucks, so we can guarantee you find the perfect vehicle for your travels. Booking with us is hassle free with our contactless Check In. It's simple, locate rental, book rental, upload pictures and GO!

To ensure our travelers have a 5-star experience we have included 2 maintenance services for all our vehicles. 

UNCLE EDS OIL SHOPPES - Travelers will have access to fast maintenance services on the go. Service includes oil changes, windshield wiper replacement, fluid top offs & tire pressure. 


(UNCLE EDS OIL SHOPPES hours)

JAX CAR WASH (FULL-SERVICE PLAN) 

Travelers will be able to get full service. This service includes interior cleaning and exterior car wash. Travelers will be able to go to any location. When you arrive at the location drive to the FULL-SERVICE LINE. Jax's carwash representatives will verify the vehicle. 

 
(Jax car wash hours) Everyday 8:00AM - 6:00PM
